{"serial": "16002", "department_serial": 16, "code": "AR0031", "class": "*", "name": {"en": "Festival And Curating Practice", "ch": "節慶活動與策展實作"}, "notice": {"en": "", "ch": ""}, "instructor": {"en": ["Huang, Lan-Yan"], "ch": ["黃蘭燕"]}, "credits": 3, "time_loc": [{"time": {"week": 4, "session": ["2", "3", "4"]}, "loc": {"building": "C2", "room": "204"}}], "isRequired": false, "isFullSem": false, "MaxStu": 50, "department": {"ch": "藝術學研究所碩士班", "en": "MA in Art Studies"}, "system": {"ch": "學士班", "en": "Undergraduate Programme"}, "language": {"ch": "國語", "en": "Chinese"}, "card": {"ch": "部份使用", "en": "Optional"}, "assigned": 0, "selected": 26, "remark": {"ch": "", "en": ""}, "goal": {"ch": "節慶活動充斥我們的生活，無論是傳統或創新的活動。這些活動亦是活絡地方經濟、復振文化、凝聚認同的方式；在節慶活動中，展示設計則為溝通文化內容的型式。而策展是說故事的方式，這個人人都需要故事的時代，用故事作文化溝通，是文化工作者的能力，本課程將培育學生策展基礎概念與入門方法。\n本課程目標在培養學生具規畫及執行文化活動的能力，包括以下目標：\n1、引導學生思考文化節慶活動的本質與內涵，包括重大節慶介紹、台灣經典節慶。\n2、帶領學生認識節慶與展覽的籌備、設計、財務、行銷、執行等各階段作業。", "en": "1. Guide students to think about the nature and connotation of cultural festivals, including introduction to major festivals and classic festivals in Taiwan.\n\n2. Lead students to understand the preparation, design, finance, marketing, and execution of festivals and exhibitions."}, "outline": {"ch": "•W1—課程介紹、作業說明\n•W2—物件的力量—成為說故事的人\n•W3—策展流程\n•W4—策展作為社會溝通的工具\n•W5—展示手法\n•W6—展覽心智圖工作坊 (移地教學—寶藏巖)\n•W7—期中分享會：個人故事箱\n•W8—節慶活動改變社會的可能：日本瀨戶內海藝術祭\n•W9—節慶活動的本質與文化意義\n•W10—節慶活動類型、規模與反思\n•W11—節慶活動與地方創生\n•W12—(課堂討論)\n•W13—跨域資源協作\n•W14—(移地教學)\n•W15—節慶活動的人力、服務、設備\n•W16—節慶活動的財務規畫、進度管理\n•W17—活動與展覽的效益評估與檢討\n•W18—期末分享會—團隊藝術行動實作", "en": "•W1—introduce\n•W2—storyteller\n•W3—Curation Process\n•W4—Curation for social communication\n•W5—display method\n•W6—Exhibition Mind Mapping Workshop\n•W7—Sharing Session: Personal Story Box\n•W8—Seto Inland Sea Art Festival\n•W9—The Essence and Cultural Significance of Festival Activities\n•W10—Festival type, scale and reflection\n•W11—Festivals and Place Creation\n•W12—class disscussion\n•W13—Cross-domain resource collaboration\n•W14—on-site teaching\n•W15—Manpower, services and equipment for festivals\n•W16—Financial planning and progress management of festival activities\n•W17—Benefit assessment and review of events and exhibitions\n•W18—the implementation of team art project"}, "textbook": {"ch": "<從直島啟航的瀨戶內海國際藝術祭>福武總一郎、北川富朗，遠流出版。2017\n<節慶與活動管理>， Johnny Allen, William O’Toole, Ian McDonnell著，五觀出版。2004", "en": "Festival and Special Event Management，Johnny Allen, William O’Toole, Robert Harris, Ian McDonnell"}, "selfCompiledRate": {"ch": "80", "en": "80"}, "instructMethod": {"ch": "講授\n研討", "en": ["Lecture", "Seminar"]}, "gradMethod": {"ch": "課堂討論20%\n個人作業25%\n藝術行動40%\n出席率15%", "en": "discussion 20%\nhomework 25%\nart project 40%\nAttendance rate15%"}, "officeHour": {"ch": "周四，早上8-9點", "en": "thu.8-9AM"}, "teachWeeks": {"ch": "18", "en": "18"}, "flexDiscription": {"ch": "", "en": ""}, "domain": {"ch": "文化行政", "en": "文化行政"}, "map": {"ch": [{"competencies": "專業知能", "rating": "(4)高", "assesments": ["口頭報告/口試", "作品/創作展演"]}, {"competencies": "邏輯與批判能力", "rating": "(3)普通", "assesments": ["作業練習", "口頭報告/口試"]}, {"competencies": "語文表達與溝通", "rating": "(5)非常高", "assesments": ["口頭報告/口試"]}, {"competencies": "多元與國際視野", "rating": "(4)高", "assesments": ["作業練習", "口頭報告/口試"]}, {"competencies": "自主學習", "rating": "(5)非常高", "assesments": ["口頭報告/口試", "作品/創作展演"]}, {"competencies": "統合與創新能力", "rating": "(5)非常高", "assesments": ["口頭報告/口試", "實作/實驗", "自我評量/同儕互評"]}], "en": [{"competencies": "Professional knowledge", "rating": "(4)High", "assesments": ["Presentation/Oral Exam", "Products/Creative Performance"]}, {"competencies": "Logical and critical ability", "rating": "(3)Medium", "assesments": ["Assignments", "Presentation/Oral Exam"]}, {"competencies": "Ability to communicate clearly", "rating": "(5)VeryHigh", "assesments": ["Presentation/Oral Exam"]}, {"competencies": "A diverse and international vision", "rating": "(4)High", "assesments": ["Assignments", "Presentation/Oral Exam"]}, {"competencies": "Self-in